data.description: Escape to your idyllic country living haven. This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-full-bath house rests on over half an acre of lush landscape. The rustic charm meets modern comfort, offering a serene living space with abundant natural light. Enjoy the spacious kitchen, cozy bedrooms including a master suite, and step outside to a sprawling backyard for endless outdoor activities. Embrace a tranquil lifestyle while being conveniently located. Your perfect country retreat awaits
